      <title>Japan Union Group 寻求至少 6% 的加薪以推动日本央行政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/japan-union-group-seeks-at-least-6-pay-rise-to-push-boj-policy</link>
